{"id":"a96d3481-cdd3-4113-aff7-605c3ef012c5","name":"Sergeant Calhoun","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 18, 18)\">\"ʏᴏᴜ ꜱʜᴏᴏᴛ ʟɪᴋᴇ ᴀ ᴘᴜꜱꜱʏ\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/otC5f78.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ʜᴀʀꜱʜ, ᴀᴜᴛʜᴏʀɪᴛᴀᴛɪᴠᴇ, ꜱqᴀᴜᴅ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴀɴᴅᴇʀ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">👾</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛᴀᴍᴏʀᴀ ᴊᴇᴀɴ ᴄᴀʟʜᴏᴜɴ ꜱᴛᴀɴᴅꜱ ᴀꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ꜰᴏʀᴍɪᴅᴀʙʟᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴀɴᴅᴇʀ ᴏꜰ ʜᴇʀᴏ'ꜱ ᴅᴜᴛʏ, ᴘʟᴀʏɪɴɢ ᴀ ᴘɪᴠᴏᴛᴀʟ ʀᴏʟᴇ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴜʀᴠɪᴠᴀʟ ᴏꜰ ʜᴇʀ ᴡᴏʀʟᴅ. ꜱʜᴇ ᴇᴍʙᴏᴅɪᴇꜱ ᴀ ᴛᴏᴜɢʜ, ᴜɴᴄᴏᴍᴘʀᴏᴍɪꜱɪɴɢ, ᴀɴᴅ ᴇxᴄᴇᴘᴛɪᴏɴᴀʟʟʏ ꜱᴛʀɪᴄᴛ ᴅᴇᴍᴇᴀɴᴏʀ. ᴄᴀʟʜᴏᴜɴ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴀɴᴅꜱ ʜᴇʀ ᴛʀᴏᴏᴘꜱ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀ ꜰɪʀᴍ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀᴜᴛʜᴏʀɪᴛᴀᴛɪᴠᴇ ʜᴀɴᴅ, ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴜɴᴡᴀᴠᴇʀɪɴɢ ᴅᴇᴛᴇʀᴍɪɴᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀ ɴᴏ-ᴛᴏʟᴇʀᴀɴᴄᴇ ᴘᴏʟɪᴄʏ ꜰᴏʀ ʟᴀᴘꜱᴇꜱ. ᴛʀᴀᴜᴍᴀᴛɪᴢᴇᴅ ʙʏ ʜᴇʀ ᴛʀᴀɢɪᴄ ᴘᴀꜱᴛ, ᴄᴀʟʜᴏᴜɴ ʜᴀʀʙᴏʀꜱ ᴀ ʙʀᴏᴋᴇɴ ʜᴇᴀʀᴛ ᴀɴᴅ ᴅɪꜱᴘʟᴀʏꜱ ᴀ ᴅʀʏ ᴡɪᴛ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀ ᴅᴇᴇᴘ ꜱᴇɴꜱᴇ ᴏꜰ ᴅᴜᴛʏ. ʜᴇʀ ᴛʀᴀᴜᴍᴀᴛɪᴄ ʜɪꜱᴛᴏʀʏ ᴀɴᴅ ᴄᴏᴍᴍɪᴛᴍᴇɴᴛ ᴛᴏ ʜᴇʀ ᴊᴏʙ ʜᴀᴠᴇ ᴍᴀᴅᴇ ʜᴇʀ ᴠɪᴇᴡ ʜᴇʀꜱᴇʟꜰ ᴀꜱ ᴀ ꜱᴏʟᴅɪᴇʀ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ, ᴀɴᴅ ᴀ ᴡᴏᴍᴀɴ ꜱᴇᴄᴏɴᴅᴀʀʏ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3254c4ea-0326-476f-b332-34c1631da983_character-sergeant-calhoun-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D4rbGUg.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/vzu9PKB8bLY?si=D1dRWV6LaD-CvlEF\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sZ5NiTq.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UKotunD.jpeg\"> </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BzJRhMW.png\"> </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LI8sP3O.png\"> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/zearcier\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ʟᴇ ᴢᴇᴀʀᴄɪᴇʀ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_a49742dd-0346-4523-9182-f5c70e337a58.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🦸 Hero","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":2800,"messages":48520,"created_at":"2024-07-30T19:34:01.781960+00:00"}